<paragraph id="A96BC66334924008BF74F5110FFD7757" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">Aufrechte Wolfsmilch</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="D10EAA518FD51B9894984BD2C29DAC84" pageId="null" pageNumber="661" type="description">
<paragraph id="8D5AD3C0C6A73CB404B323DF651521B4" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="A0AEAA275615D2990DDD9FCD000A851D" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="Euphorbia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="661" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="platyphyllos">
<emphasis id="A6C8E55A207BE077928AEA2A00DEC2E8" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">E. platyphyllos</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 8) durch folgende Merkmale: Pflanze 1 
<normalizedToken id="B9D1E57470197F3EDC5D0923148B0B37" originalValue="jährig" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">jaehrig</normalizedToken>
oder ausdauernd, oft mit mehreren Stengeln; Stiele 1. Ordnung des 
<normalizedToken id="64ED0595FFB2824DAD0ED7250462D2B5" originalValue="endständigen" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">endstaendigen</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="C139351EC924D86F5EEC44101A2A0C43" originalValue="Gesamtblütenstandes" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">Gesamtbluetenstandes</normalizedToken>
<pageBreakToken id="8D66354C9F34FECF7DC7F91EEA9C5AA1" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">stets</pageBreakToken>
vielfach gabelig verzweigt; 
<emphasis id="2B52F34F45101FEDD04EF7A7A637410A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">
Frucht 
<normalizedToken id="B2589946CB3904A70120D15839D96A34" originalValue="überall" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">ueberall</normalizedToken>
mit Warzen besetzt; Warzen zylindrisch; Same 1,2
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="B0311ABD76CDD1E7F629A69499B3F52E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">1,6 mm lang und 0,9</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="C59433925D75A98B6C092E048A6957FA" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">1,1 mm dick.</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="070F0A5C2D6AA9949A98A6931D8ACFF2" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="EDA4E9C54E4C70B97ECABB64DFA6884B" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">
<emphasis id="AE35CE69A4C243D7E5800F7A67A89741" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="01D1D920C8252BF97A125D109050B2D2" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">28:</emphasis>
Material aus der Schweiz (Perry 1943).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C4580FE266ABE8DCEA96D2F525D905FA" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">
<emphasis id="521E3992E9C86025AB34A05A3B39DFE1" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin, selten montan. Feuchte, 
<normalizedToken id="38700B6129C845C601126DDEAB840E7F" originalValue="nährstoffreiche" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">naehrstoffreiche</normalizedToken>
, kalkhaltige, sandige bis lehmige 
<normalizedToken id="A03350A824D61630C497D8DC854E967F" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">Boeden</normalizedToken>
. 
<normalizedToken id="D4F930553AE71F58BA20E4383F37228D" originalValue="Auenwälder" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">Auenwaelder</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="6E403558655141B2775FB82B9DE5F440" originalValue="Waldschläge" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">Waldschlaege</normalizedToken>
, Waldwege, 
<normalizedToken id="EBB849A53DF346A28AFEF8D8250C5953" originalValue="Waldränder" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">Waldraender</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="08D265B86F3D25FF034571A6C66EA7E1" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">
<emphasis id="A6E250B7537F58B97FD1D1A342D68CCE" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken id="F09C6F931F4C62B6B1A8BB715A7307A2" originalValue="Europäisch-westasiatische" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">Europaeisch-westasiatische</normalizedToken>
Pflanze:
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="44C14BD4EFDD126D8C2F797F7B31C76A" originalValue="Nordwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">Nordwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis England, Niederrhein, Main, Donau, Oder (Frankfurt), 
<normalizedToken id="89342CE37BAC90E170CE3D9114E3BC71" originalValue="südliche" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">suedliche</normalizedToken>
Weichsel, 
<normalizedToken id="C2D1D8FCF0D441024E55F0DC1C5A9AE8" originalValue="Mittelrußland" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">Mittelrussland</normalizedToken>
; 
<normalizedToken id="31C65531C1D9998D0458402C8FC3BAC7" originalValue="ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Wolgagebiet und Aralsee; 
<normalizedToken id="BD424610BEE098F35A20BDEAFFE53983" originalValue="südwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">suedwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis 
<normalizedToken id="2CB664DADE8F2EEE7FF1A9EC3B208259" originalValue="Pyrenäen" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">Pyrenaeen</normalizedToken>
, Norditalien, Griechenland, Krim, Kaukasus, Nordiran. - Im Gebiet verbreitet, ziemlich 
<normalizedToken id="8800576B870AFBB560AD2D6B383A6A5F" originalValue="häufig" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">haeufig</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="FB3E1B32FCCB110601289F884863DD85" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">
<emphasis id="C6201DDCDA54F57BC9AEB53268F7B23C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">Bemerkungen.</emphasis>
In &quot;Flora Europaea&quot; 
<emphasis id="11F5109418E206CDDD86556F46F29981" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">2</emphasis>
(1968) wird der Name 
<taxonomicName id="04CB7D003FB97C09937E293C27154965" authority="Thuill." authorityName="Thuill." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="Euphorbia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="661" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="serrulata">
<emphasis id="0B58254EC4A7B4DDB9D0E49A6F28F059" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="661">E. serrulata</emphasis>
Thuill.
</taxonomicName>
verwendet.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
